2
00:00:47.740 --> 00:00:51.920
"Five hundred dollars for
the death of Chen Kuo-Wei."

3
00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.480
Hey. Friend!

4
00:01:17.150 --> 00:01:20.190
Your style's not bad.
But take it easy. you look beat.

5
00:01:23.950 --> 00:01:28.350
You must be the Four Door Fist Champion.

6
00:01:28.351 --> 00:01:29.527
Chen Kuo-Wei?

7
00:01:31.075 --> 00:01:34.465
Yes I am. and who might you be?

8
00:01:34.750 --> 00:01:36.943
I'm Yen Tieh-hsin.

9
00:01:39.675 --> 00:01:42.473
I've heard of your devil's kick.

10
00:01:42.475 --> 00:01:46.601
It's famous in the Kung-Fu world.
It has never been defeated...

11
00:01:48.350 --> 00:01:49.680
And it never will.

12
00:01:50.750 --> 00:01:51.904
I suppose I should warn you.

13
00:01:53.350 --> 00:01:55.997
I've been given good money to kill you.

14
00:01:56.800 --> 00:02:00.223
What the hell are you talking about?
Someone's paid you to kill me?

15
00:02:00.225 --> 00:02:02.455
I'll give you twice as much to kill him!

16
00:02:03.525 --> 00:02:06.948
You could. only my honour comes first.

17
00:02:06.950 --> 00:02:10.628
You must realize I'm paid to kill.
The contract's sealed.

18
00:02:10.629 --> 00:02:13.273
- So you must die.
- Don't be so sure of that...

19
00:02:13.275 --> 00:02:17.754
For I. champion of the four Door Fists.
have never yet been defeated!

20
00:02:18.567 --> 00:02:23.364
I don't care who you are. I'll break every
bone in your body and send you to hell.

21
00:03:25.609 --> 00:03:27.625
"Wong Kei-Ying Martial Art School"

22
00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:46.755
Kai Hsien!

23
00:03:50.354 --> 00:03:54.623
- What's the matter. Master?
- I'm going out. keep an eye on them.

24
00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:55.665
Yes. sir.

25
00:04:03.117 --> 00:04:04.074
Stop!

26
00:04:06.625 --> 00:04:08.815
We won't practice this today.

27
00:04:09.425 --> 00:04:13.607
Let's practice the Fist of Five Styles
which I taught you a few days ago.

28
00:04:13.609 --> 00:04:14.811
He's so lame...

29
00:04:14.813 --> 00:04:16.580
- Three-legged cat.
- Four-eyed rat.

30
00:04:17.150 --> 00:04:18.580
Start now.

31
00:04:20.050 --> 00:04:22.748
Dragon Sees Tiger.

32
00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:25.960
Tiger's rear. Snake's Tongue Darts Out.

33
00:04:26.750 --> 00:04:28.221
Panther Sees Fire.

34
00:04:28.975 --> 00:04:31.430
White Crane Spreads Wings.

35
00:04:32.425 --> 00:04:33.657
Hold it!

36
00:04:36.740 --> 00:04:41.460
Your wrists are too weak.
You can't learn it well. understand?

37
00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:22.654
I suppose you think that was funny.
playing tricks on your teacher!

38
00:05:22.656 --> 00:05:24.656
We'll see. Take that! And that!

39
00:05:25.671 --> 00:05:28.098
- It wasn't me!
- Who was it? Tell me.

40
00:05:28.100 --> 00:05:29.548
Who was it?

41
00:05:29.550 --> 00:05:31.266
- Wong Fei-Hung.
- What?

42
00:05:37.674 --> 00:05:38.754
Wong Fei-Hung.

43
00:05:40.253 --> 00:05:43.248
Even though Master Wong is your father.

44
00:05:43.250 --> 00:05:45.710
you don't have a right
to cause trouble here.

45
00:05:45.712 --> 00:05:48.560
You think Kung-Fu is
just a performance.

46
00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:52.523
You're telling me my Kung-Fu is bad?

47
00:05:52.525 --> 00:05:55.004
Not too bad. but bad enough.

48
00:05:56.282 --> 00:05:59.420
Show me exactly what's wrong with it.

49
00:06:00.896 --> 00:06:03.190
Look at your Panther Sees Fire.

50
00:06:03.192 --> 00:06:04.054
Well what's wrong?

51
00:06:04.056 --> 00:06:07.596
You've exposed your body.
It's easy to attack you.

52
00:06:08.231 --> 00:06:13.256
And that Horse Stance is
bow-legged. Just a kick...

53
00:06:16.225 --> 00:06:18.335
and you'll fall.

54
00:06:29.700 --> 00:06:32.510
Shut up! Shut up you turkeys!

55
00:06:36.173 --> 00:06:39.248
You'd like to test your
teacher's Kung-Fu. would you?

56
00:06:39.250 --> 00:06:41.870
We can all learn from each other.

57
00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:49.356
I can stand almost anything. you bum!
But I've taken enough of this bullshit!

58
00:06:57.453 --> 00:06:59.853
You've exposed your body again.
Do you know that. teacher?

59
00:07:03.775 --> 00:07:04.855
Your hat!

60
00:07:09.025 --> 00:07:10.037
Here you go!

61
00:07:27.900 --> 00:07:29.520
Pork belly. shut up!

62
00:07:37.700 --> 00:07:39.974
Look! Right foot! Snake stance!

63
00:07:41.922 --> 00:07:43.566
Bastard!

64
00:07:51.589 --> 00:07:55.622
Wong Fei-Hung.
you've taught Hsien a lesson.

65
00:07:55.624 --> 00:07:57.621
We all feel very happy about it.

66
00:07:57.623 --> 00:08:00.897
He's too arrogant. I can't stand it.

67
00:08:01.430 --> 00:08:03.740
You really showed him!

68
00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:12.350
That's great...

69
00:08:13.939 --> 00:08:15.585
Eat more then!

70
00:08:15.587 --> 00:08:18.289
No. I'm talking about that girl.

71
00:08:18.291 --> 00:08:22.650
That perfect frame she's got.
Really sexy!

72
00:08:23.712 --> 00:08:25.042
- How much?
- 30 cents.

73
00:08:25.706 --> 00:08:27.123
Not bad!

74
00:08:27.125 --> 00:08:30.580
I'm willing to trade 10 years
just for a kiss by her!

75
00:08:30.582 --> 00:08:34.675
Kissing is for children.
I could get her to hug and kiss me.

76
00:08:35.338 --> 00:08:36.709
I don't believe you!

77
00:08:36.711 --> 00:08:39.360
You want to bet on it?
I’ll bet you a whole dinner.

78
00:08:39.362 --> 00:08:41.013
Deal.

79
00:08:41.015 --> 00:08:45.275
She's hot. she wouldn't
look at you twice!

80
00:08:46.781 --> 00:08:48.521
All right! A whole dinner then.

81
00:08:54.675 --> 00:08:55.795
Just watch.

82
00:08:56.984 --> 00:08:58.074
He's looking for trouble.

83
00:08:59.287 --> 00:09:05.472
This flower is beautiful.
Trust me. try it on.

84
00:09:05.474 --> 00:09:07.758
- Excuse me!
- My eye hurts.

85
00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:08.856
What can I do?

86
00:09:08.858 --> 00:09:13.800
Something got into my eye.
Help me get rid of it. miss. Please. hurry

87
00:09:15.965 --> 00:09:17.215
Harder.

88
00:09:19.618 --> 00:09:21.865
- He did it!
- Did you see that?

89
00:09:21.867 --> 00:09:23.717
Thanks. Snake!

90
00:09:26.186 --> 00:09:28.915
Don't be afraid...
I'll kill it. Don't be afraid.

91
00:09:30.115 --> 00:09:31.615
That's a great technique.

92
00:09:31.617 --> 00:09:34.543
That's great. I must try
that on your sister.

93
00:09:34.545 --> 00:09:36.155
What did you say? My sister?

94
00:09:39.951 --> 00:09:43.085
Thought you could take advantage
of my daughter. did you?

95
00:09:46.267 --> 00:09:51.106
Me touch her? She was asking
for it. that dumb bitch.

96
00:09:51.108 --> 00:09:51.923
Mother!

97
00:09:51.925 --> 00:09:54.973
You wanted to lay your
filthy hands on her.

98
00:09:54.975 --> 00:09:58.435
On her? That's a laugh.
She's much too ugly.

99
00:09:59.299 --> 00:10:02.642
Think you’re real smart. huh?
Well. I’ll teach you a lesson. boy.

100
00:10:14.400 --> 00:10:17.295
So you want to play Kung-Fu? Try this!

101
00:10:31.525 --> 00:10:32.974
The old bitch is tough.

102
00:10:37.184 --> 00:10:39.487
Come on. you guys! Hey!

103
00:10:41.162 --> 00:10:42.400
Some friends they make.

104
00:10:56.344 --> 00:10:59.628
You're nothing but a skinny old woman.
so I'll let you win.

105
00:10:59.630 --> 00:11:00.374
Excuse me!

106
00:11:15.682 --> 00:11:18.002
Watch where you’re going!

107
00:11:18.004 --> 00:11:19.900
Stumbling about like a drunken stooge!

108
00:11:23.884 --> 00:11:25.722
Antique jade!

109
00:11:26.834 --> 00:11:28.834
Mister. want to buy?

110
00:11:32.002 --> 00:11:33.003
You sure it's real?

111
00:11:33.100 --> 00:11:34.487
Of course.

112
00:11:34.489 --> 00:11:38.133
It’s a family heirloom.
It's worth the money. sir.

113
00:11:38.135 --> 00:11:40.713
- How much?
- 10 dollars.

114
00:11:40.715 --> 00:11:41.735
That's too expensive!

115
00:11:43.319 --> 00:11:44.318
It’s worth it!

116
00:11:46.786 --> 00:11:49.586
Only 10 cents?! Hey mister!

117
00:11:49.588 --> 00:11:54.023
Mister. I can't sell it that cheap.
Please give it back to me. It’s all I have!

118
00:11:54.025 --> 00:11:57.444
I couldn't sell such a
valuable piece for only 10 cents!

119
00:11:57.446 --> 00:11:59.202
Then I’ll keep the jade and the money.

120
00:12:00.147 --> 00:12:01.361
Hey. give me back my jade.

121
00:12:04.105 --> 00:12:07.403
Mister. you broke my jade!
Pay me back!

122
00:12:07.405 --> 00:12:09.965
You expect payment from me? Take this!

123
00:12:09.967 --> 00:12:11.679
Father...

124
00:12:11.681 --> 00:12:14.385
Please. at least give me something.

125
00:12:18.689 --> 00:12:19.633
What happened?

126
00:12:19.635 --> 00:12:23.651
He's broken my jade and
then he refused to pay me!

127
00:12:27.284 --> 00:12:28.637
Shithead. Piss off.

128
00:12:29.703 --> 00:12:31.015
Who're you calling Shithead?

129
00:12:31.394 --> 00:12:32.514
I'm calling you!

130
00:12:35.549 --> 00:12:37.497
Hand over that man's money!

131
00:12:37.499 --> 00:12:40.472
Pay? Not before I put you in the ground.

132
00:12:40.474 --> 00:12:42.331
It's too bad you feel that way.

133
00:12:42.928 --> 00:12:47.798
There's nothing been going right today.
so you caught me in a bad mood.

134
00:12:47.800 --> 00:12:49.711
Now. I'm gonna have to
teach you how to pay!

135
00:13:00.084 --> 00:13:01.134
Get up!

136
00:13:22.334 --> 00:13:23.314
Wanna kill me?

137
00:13:36.775 --> 00:13:37.960
This is dangerous!

138
00:13:49.433 --> 00:13:50.913
You barely missed my knuckles!

139
00:13:59.125 --> 00:14:01.145
- This is for you. now get going!
- Thank you. sir.

140
00:14:14.325 --> 00:14:17.623
I'm doomed. I'm dead!

141
00:14:17.625 --> 00:14:19.405
Don't be afraid.
it's just the blunt end.

142
00:14:24.198 --> 00:14:26.773
I have no intention of killing you...

143
00:14:26.775 --> 00:14:27.774
...yet!

144
00:14:32.740 --> 00:14:33.972
Don't...!

145
00:14:36.984 --> 00:14:38.544
That one really came close.

146
00:14:39.675 --> 00:14:41.595
And watch what you're doing.

147
00:14:43.425 --> 00:14:44.424
Drop dead!

148
00:14:55.425 --> 00:15:00.335
Fists have no eyes. knives have no heart!
Sometimes I can hit by mistake!

149
00:15:03.505 --> 00:15:06.228
I chop. chop. chop... the meat!

150
00:15:06.230 --> 00:15:08.753
I slice. slice. slice... like a cucumber!

151
00:15:08.755 --> 00:15:11.712
I beat. beat. beat... you like garlic!

152
00:15:12.368 --> 00:15:15.048
I’m glad I came across you.
You sure have brightened my day!

153
00:15:22.062 --> 00:15:26.452
It’s been ages. brother.
You still look great.

154
00:15:27.425 --> 00:15:29.839
Your brother is old now.

155
00:15:29.841 --> 00:15:32.727
What a beautiful niece I’ve got.

156
00:15:33.143 --> 00:15:36.323
She's still a kid. Just a bit naive.

157
00:15:37.777 --> 00:15:38.745
Where's Fei-Hung?

158
00:15:39.253 --> 00:15:40.492
He went out.

159
00:15:40.494 --> 00:15:43.989
This naughty boy always goes out to play.
He's a young man now.

160
00:15:43.991 --> 00:15:45.991
I think you may not recognize him.

161
00:15:47.384 --> 00:15:49.364
This time. stay longer.

162
00:15:50.490 --> 00:15:52.100
Fei-Hung. don't go away.

163
00:15:52.496 --> 00:15:54.496
Come greet your auntie and cousin.

164
00:15:58.302 --> 00:15:59.563
Come here. now.

165
00:15:59.565 --> 00:16:00.635
Coming...

166
00:16:01.097 --> 00:16:02.097
Shit!

167
00:16:11.337 --> 00:16:12.407
Say hello.

168
00:16:13.843 --> 00:16:15.943
Auntie. cousin.

169
00:16:16.103 --> 00:16:17.906
- Cousin.
- Fei-Hung.

170
00:16:18.384 --> 00:16:19.475
What happened to your neck?

171
00:16:19.865 --> 00:16:22.191
I... I slept without a pillow.

172
00:16:22.672 --> 00:16:26.101
Without a pillow? Let me help you.

173
00:16:26.103 --> 00:16:30.353
- No thanks. auntie.
- Come on. relax.

174
00:16:31.618 --> 00:16:32.617
Auntie.

175
00:16:34.065 --> 00:16:35.064
Mother!

176
00:16:36.522 --> 00:16:37.672
Feel better now?

177
00:16:37.843 --> 00:16:38.943
Yes.

178
00:16:42.450 --> 00:16:43.710
Brother.

179
00:16:43.712 --> 00:16:46.003
Fei-Hung really looks smart.

180
00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:50.665
He's quite tactful and clever.

181
00:16:52.502 --> 00:16:55.225
Brother. you're really a good father.

182
00:16:55.666 --> 00:16:58.316
Yes. I’m very strict to him.

183
00:16:58.984 --> 00:17:03.474
No wonder I heard people praising
him as soon as I came here.

184
00:17:03.820 --> 00:17:06.054
Really? What did they say?

185
00:17:06.056 --> 00:17:10.342
The son of Wong Kei-Ying is very smart.

186
00:17:10.344 --> 00:17:11.966
He's also a man of justice.

187
00:17:13.253 --> 00:17:16.743
I’m very proud of him.
Come here. my son.

188
00:17:21.281 --> 00:17:22.281
Sit down.

189
00:17:24.425 --> 00:17:28.785
But there are many sex
maniacs in this village.

190
00:17:30.175 --> 00:17:31.273
That's right.

191
00:17:31.275 --> 00:17:34.900
One of them harassed your
niece on the street just now.

192
00:17:34.902 --> 00:17:38.925
when I went to rescue her.
he even attacked me.

193
00:17:40.318 --> 00:17:44.177
You mean to tell me both of you
were attacked here in my own town?

194
00:17:44.618 --> 00:17:45.617
Could you recognize him?

195
00:17:49.050 --> 00:17:51.373
As if I could forget.
Yes. I'd recognize him.

196
00:17:51.375 --> 00:17:53.595
Good. let's find him now.

197
00:17:54.025 --> 00:17:56.985
I’ll teach him a real good lesson.
Fei-Hung. come with me.

198
00:17:58.325 --> 00:18:00.673
Uncle! You don't have to go out.

199
00:18:00.675 --> 00:18:01.473
Why?

200
00:18:01.475 --> 00:18:04.195
That guy is right here.
He's standing in this very room.

201
00:18:04.590 --> 00:18:05.773
Who? Where?

202
00:18:05.775 --> 00:18:08.865
Standing right over there.
He's your son. Wong Fei-Hung.

203
00:18:12.200 --> 00:18:13.199
You...

204
00:18:14.625 --> 00:18:15.624
You...

205
00:18:16.867 --> 00:18:18.357
Son-of-bitch!

206
00:18:20.475 --> 00:18:21.655
Kneel down!

207
00:18:22.225 --> 00:18:23.328
Father...

208
00:18:23.330 --> 00:18:24.663
You bastard!

209
00:18:24.665 --> 00:18:26.265
You have dishonoured me.

210
00:18:30.531 --> 00:18:31.530
Wong Kei-Ying!

211
00:18:33.802 --> 00:18:34.831
I'm doomed.

212
00:18:47.375 --> 00:18:48.725
Wong Kei-Ying.

213
00:18:48.725 --> 00:18:50.805
Master Li. what has happened?

214
00:18:51.759 --> 00:18:54.579
I'll tell you what.
I'm looking for your son.

215
00:18:58.550 --> 00:18:59.650
Why?

216
00:19:00.756 --> 00:19:02.363
Because he's nothing but a wild animal.

217
00:19:02.365 --> 00:19:07.045
He attacked my son for no reason.
breaking his legs. arms. and skull.

218
00:19:09.281 --> 00:19:11.494
He really beat him up.

219
00:19:12.040 --> 00:19:13.834
He looks like a dumpling.

220
00:19:14.199 --> 00:19:16.289
Wong Kei-Ying! I want justice!

221
00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:23.505
- You beast. I must kill you.
- No. Dad... No...

222
00:19:25.325 --> 00:19:26.951
Brother. you mustn't kill your own son.

223
00:19:26.953 --> 00:19:27.954
Yes!

224
00:19:28.225 --> 00:19:30.668
I must kill him. he's a disgrace!

225
00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:36.660
Sounds bad for a teacher of your
standing to flog his own son to death.

226
00:19:37.404 --> 00:19:40.784
Mr. Li didn't come to witness
how you punish your son.

227
00:19:41.075 --> 00:19:44.325
If he must be punished. I suggest
that Mr. Li here is quite capable.

228
00:19:46.575 --> 00:19:48.095
Stop him!

229
00:19:49.225 --> 00:19:52.338
I’m responsible for what I’ve done.
So let him punish me.

230
00:19:53.265 --> 00:19:54.785
Take this.

231
00:19:55.425 --> 00:19:57.685
Now. I promise I won't fight back.

232
00:19:59.825 --> 00:20:01.685
You dare make fun at this time?

233
00:20:02.125 --> 00:20:04.825
Wong Kei-Ying. what are you gonna do?

234
00:20:05.650 --> 00:20:08.280
As from this moment. I disown him.

235
00:20:08.775 --> 00:20:12.235
This slime is no longer mine.
Do what you like with him.

236
00:20:15.496 --> 00:20:17.550
Mr. Li. I have a proposition.

237
00:20:17.978 --> 00:20:20.688
Let Fei-hung take ten strikes
without any resistance.

238
00:20:21.330 --> 00:20:25.702
Ten strikes should be enough.
Now. Mr. Li. do you approve?

239
00:20:28.393 --> 00:20:31.823
I don't need ten strikes
to kill him. three is enough.

240
00:20:34.984 --> 00:20:38.464
Master. listen.
I’m going to fix that squirt.

241
00:20:38.806 --> 00:20:42.756
Master Chao. be sure you leave
him looking just like I look now.

242
00:21:31.828 --> 00:21:33.008
The Divine Eight.

243
00:21:33.010 --> 00:21:36.045
That palm style of yours.
it's really something.

244
00:21:36.687 --> 00:21:37.786
I’m only getting started!

245
00:21:47.862 --> 00:21:48.932
I'm not dead yet!

246
00:21:56.621 --> 00:21:58.071
You want to cut off my posterity?

247
00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:11.880
Enough!

248
00:22:13.973 --> 00:22:16.193
You've made your ten strikes. Mr. Chow.

249
00:22:18.025 --> 00:22:20.125
You said you would kill
me within three strikes.

250
00:22:25.400 --> 00:22:26.860
Snake and Crane together.

251
00:22:29.862 --> 00:22:31.122
Strike the vital points.

252
00:22:35.140 --> 00:22:37.090
Let's try your Divine Eight again.

253
00:22:49.707 --> 00:22:51.157
I told you I’ve got style.

254
00:23:41.953 --> 00:23:43.763
Hey! My jacket's getting dirty. take it!

255
00:23:56.700 --> 00:23:59.190
You regret not paying
for that jade now. huh!

256
00:24:01.344 --> 00:24:04.026
- It's me!
- You hit your master.

257
00:24:09.380 --> 00:24:13.780
- Young Master. are you alright?
- Young master. are you okay?

258
00:24:26.576 --> 00:24:30.046
Master. now I look just like you.

259
00:24:32.378 --> 00:24:33.773
Wong Kei-Ying.

260
00:24:33.775 --> 00:24:36.898
you win with your smart tricks.

261
00:24:36.900 --> 00:24:37.899
I'll get you back.

262
00:24:37.900 --> 00:24:39.010
Let's go!

263
00:24:39.012 --> 00:24:40.032
You watch out!

264
00:24:40.840 --> 00:24:43.764
Careful with my son. hurry.

265
00:24:43.766 --> 00:24:45.740
- I'll get you yet!
- So don't come back!

266
00:24:47.415 --> 00:24:48.905
Careful. careful.

267
00:24:52.175 --> 00:24:55.155
He came in with one cripple
and left with two.

268
00:24:56.125 --> 00:24:59.098
You fight well. I give you that.

269
00:24:59.100 --> 00:25:00.945
- But I'll still kill you!
- Brother.

270
00:25:02.300 --> 00:25:04.948
It’s useless to beat him anymore.

271
00:25:04.950 --> 00:25:06.770
Let's punish him by Kung-Fu practice.

272
00:25:07.447 --> 00:25:09.373
I’ve tried with that bastard.

273
00:25:09.375 --> 00:25:10.298
Right!

274
00:25:10.300 --> 00:25:12.533
From now on. you are forbidden
to leave the house.

275
00:25:13.400 --> 00:25:15.179
We'll start with five
hours of Horse Stance!

276
00:26:05.422 --> 00:26:06.502
Now don't move.

277
00:26:08.415 --> 00:26:11.735
Have some more boiling water. bastard!

278
00:26:17.181 --> 00:26:20.690
Hey. are you comfortable?

279
00:26:24.571 --> 00:26:30.354
Are your legs shaking. are they aching?
You know. I feel sorry for you.

280
00:26:30.356 --> 00:26:32.156
Poor little chicken!

281
00:26:40.314 --> 00:26:43.634
You feel itchy? Want me to help you?

282
00:26:50.346 --> 00:26:53.676
Stop. Don't do that!

283
00:26:54.175 --> 00:26:58.305
I'm just carrying out my orders.
See. it's your father's idea.

284
00:26:58.307 --> 00:27:02.377
He says for every bowl you break.
you stay another hour.

285
00:27:02.379 --> 00:27:03.560
you bastard!

286
00:27:53.660 --> 00:27:55.760
Master. you're back!

287
00:28:00.965 --> 00:28:03.425
Yes. his stance appears
to be pretty steady.

288
00:28:04.154 --> 00:28:09.246
- Did he slack off?
- No. I’ve been watching him.

289
00:28:09.248 --> 00:28:10.353
Really?

290
00:28:11.765 --> 00:28:13.255
Finally some progress.

291
00:28:13.257 --> 00:28:15.787
Yes. I'm very tired.

292
00:28:16.987 --> 00:28:19.152
- Are you really that tired?
- I am. sir.

293
00:28:19.842 --> 00:28:21.841
But you've got a chair. right?

294
00:28:22.951 --> 00:28:27.197
What? A chair? Let me see!
Damn it. a chair...

295
00:28:29.216 --> 00:28:32.506
You dare cheat me
when I'm punishing you.

296
00:28:35.059 --> 00:28:36.859
I really can't do anything about you.

297
00:28:37.531 --> 00:28:40.081
I’ll ask your uncle to come
tomorrow and fix you.

298
00:28:40.575 --> 00:28:41.575
Who's he?

299
00:28:42.018 --> 00:28:43.337
Beggar So.

300
00:29:06.598 --> 00:29:09.042
Help me. To Tao!

301
00:29:11.375 --> 00:29:12.738
Hurry!

302
00:29:20.525 --> 00:29:22.198
Practicing your Kung-Fu upside down. huh!

303
00:29:22.200 --> 00:29:24.925
- I'm dying!
- Here. I brought you food.

304
00:29:29.375 --> 00:29:30.705
I’ll go get something to drink.

305
00:29:31.700 --> 00:29:33.000
My neck!

306
00:29:33.550 --> 00:29:34.840
Get me down. quickly.

307
00:29:47.925 --> 00:29:49.943
Come on. get up.

308
00:29:51.509 --> 00:29:53.311
You came down so quickly.

309
00:29:54.584 --> 00:29:55.584
Untie me!

310
00:30:04.934 --> 00:30:05.933
Eat this.

311
00:30:07.350 --> 00:30:10.782
Hey. is it true So Hui
is gonna fix you?

312
00:30:10.784 --> 00:30:13.654
- That's right.
- That's bad news for you.

313
00:30:13.850 --> 00:30:14.880
Why?

314
00:30:15.168 --> 00:30:16.738
Do you know anything about Beggar So?

315
00:30:18.075 --> 00:30:19.535
I heard he's very cruel.

316
00:30:20.509 --> 00:30:23.459
All his students have if not
broken arms then broken legs!

317
00:30:24.069 --> 00:30:24.973
Really?

318
00:30:24.975 --> 00:30:26.555
I'm telling you the truth.

319
00:30:27.066 --> 00:30:32.779
Nui was his student and you
know what happened to him?

320
00:30:32.781 --> 00:30:33.841
What?

321
00:30:34.605 --> 00:30:38.849
He lost all his teeth and hair.
His nose got twisted.

322
00:30:38.850 --> 00:30:40.623
Even his own father
couldn't recognize him.

323
00:30:41.024 --> 00:30:45.434
That monster gets pleasure out of
torturing people. he's a real sadist.

324
00:30:47.537 --> 00:30:51.077
- What should I do then?
- You think about it yourself.

325
00:30:52.212 --> 00:30:55.882
You've got to help me.
I don't know what to do!

326
00:31:05.225 --> 00:31:08.325
- Escape. that's the only way!
- Escape. that's the only way!

327
00:31:09.583 --> 00:31:11.413
You're clumsy!

328
00:31:11.415 --> 00:31:12.823
You should try to pay more attention!

329
00:31:12.825 --> 00:31:15.577
- Just go.
- I’ll leave now.

330
00:31:17.538 --> 00:31:19.284
"Yue He Restaurant"

331
00:31:19.286 --> 00:31:20.686
Sir. here are the dumplings.

332
00:31:24.725 --> 00:31:26.305
Please have a seat.

333
00:31:41.850 --> 00:31:44.123
Excuse me. do you mind if I sit here?

334
00:31:44.125 --> 00:31:46.185
No. sit down. Go on.

335
00:31:47.325 --> 00:31:50.925
You're by yourself. good.
I don't like to eat alone.

336
00:31:52.900 --> 00:31:54.673
The food here is very good.

337
00:31:54.675 --> 00:31:57.035
Everything looks and tastes great.

338
00:31:58.478 --> 00:32:01.178
Real good smell. really fantastic.

339
00:32:04.025 --> 00:32:05.045
What can I get you. sir?

340
00:32:06.214 --> 00:32:08.873
Why you're alone? Where's Old Shang?

341
00:32:08.875 --> 00:32:10.525
- What's that?
- No. go ahead. eat.

342
00:32:10.778 --> 00:32:12.398
What would you like to eat?

343
00:32:13.775 --> 00:32:15.699
A bowl of shark's fin as appetizer.

344
00:32:15.701 --> 00:32:18.791
- Sorry. We got no shark's fin.
- That's too bad.

345
00:32:18.793 --> 00:32:23.205
Then I want a roasted goose leg. The left one.
A chicken and a steamed grouper.

346
00:32:23.207 --> 00:32:27.388
- Sorry. we have no grouper.
- Then any fish will do.

347
00:32:27.390 --> 00:32:29.895
Also a stewed abalone and
shrimp noodles. Hurry!

348
00:32:32.225 --> 00:32:34.186
And half a catty of
Shaoxing wine. hurry!

349
00:32:34.188 --> 00:32:35.624
One wine!

350
00:32:36.290 --> 00:32:38.430
You have a great appetite.

351
00:32:39.179 --> 00:32:43.069
It is necessary to eat
well to become strong!

352
00:33:00.697 --> 00:33:04.607
Here's the left goose leg. chicken...

353
00:33:07.312 --> 00:33:10.022
- Half litter of Shaoxing wine.
- Yes... no thanks

354
00:33:11.328 --> 00:33:14.978
- Have a little wine. Be my guest.
- Really. I...

355
00:33:18.364 --> 00:33:22.459
Here. just taste that.

356
00:33:22.461 --> 00:33:23.770
Eat up!

357
00:33:23.772 --> 00:33:26.773
Go on. don't be shy.
Help yourself to what you want.

358
00:33:26.775 --> 00:33:28.775
Enjoy yourself.
Don't stand on ceremony. Here.

359
00:33:29.939 --> 00:33:30.979
Drink...

360
00:33:40.959 --> 00:33:43.735
- Go ahead.
- I eat...

361
00:33:44.424 --> 00:33:45.844
Drink...

362
00:34:00.425 --> 00:34:02.455
You must be starving!

363
00:34:36.228 --> 00:34:37.258
Very nice.

364
00:35:04.671 --> 00:35:08.141
They sure know how to cook here.
That meal was really something.

365
00:35:08.925 --> 00:35:15.089
I’ll pay the bill. don't refuse me.
I’ll go and pay it now.

366
00:35:15.091 --> 00:35:19.214
Buy me lunch tomorrow.
I’m leaving. I’ll pay today.

367
00:35:19.216 --> 00:35:21.098
You must finish your dinner. okay?

368
00:35:21.100 --> 00:35:23.047
See you tomorrow. Bye for now.

369
00:35:24.807 --> 00:35:26.987
Take care. see you tomorrow.

370
00:35:28.412 --> 00:35:30.335
That will be exactly $1.05.

371
00:35:32.450 --> 00:35:33.848
Someone else will pay the bill.

372
00:35:33.850 --> 00:35:35.820
Really? Who?

373
00:35:38.125 --> 00:35:40.245
The old man over there.

374
00:35:43.805 --> 00:35:44.804
You know him?

375
00:35:45.705 --> 00:35:46.975
He's my father.

376
00:35:47.575 --> 00:35:48.574
Your father?

377
00:35:49.475 --> 00:35:51.345
How many fathers do you have?

378
00:35:52.712 --> 00:35:56.598
He's the boss of this
inn and I’m his son.

379
00:35:56.600 --> 00:35:57.856
That makes you a bastard.

380
00:35:59.625 --> 00:36:04.105
So you just want to eat and run?
Look there.

381
00:36:05.017 --> 00:36:06.080
"PAY OR DIE!"

382
00:36:14.000 --> 00:36:17.599
I ain't poncing meals from you.
Forgot my money. that's all.

383
00:36:17.600 --> 00:36:20.430
I’ll come back tomorrow
and pay you then.

384
00:36:32.094 --> 00:36:34.094
"PAY OR DIE!"

385
00:36:36.050 --> 00:36:38.068
Gorilla. beat him up!

386
00:37:02.563 --> 00:37:03.499
Tiger's Claw.

387
00:37:35.425 --> 00:37:37.795
No. hold it. stop. Let's talk.

388
00:37:39.250 --> 00:37:40.249
Stop it.

389
00:37:46.125 --> 00:37:48.671
Go ahead. beat him.

390
00:37:49.300 --> 00:37:51.849
I'll get back what you've eaten. Now!

391
00:37:58.858 --> 00:38:02.188
Roasted goose's leg. The left one.

392
00:38:05.699 --> 00:38:08.231
And the fish.

393
00:38:08.233 --> 00:38:09.487
That's enough.

394
00:38:10.425 --> 00:38:12.305
Also half a catty of Shaoxing wine.

395
00:38:16.800 --> 00:38:19.642
Now that you emptied my belly.
I feel hungry again.

396
00:38:30.375 --> 00:38:34.575
Hey. that's enough.
or do you want to kill the boy?

397
00:38:34.950 --> 00:38:38.439
No. it's not enough. He is to
do the toilet cleaning for us.

398
00:38:42.675 --> 00:38:43.985
You wanted something to clean?

399
00:38:51.318 --> 00:38:53.790
Thanks old man.

400
00:38:54.893 --> 00:38:58.041
Old bum! How you dare
interfere with our business!

401
00:38:58.043 --> 00:39:00.653
Just look how strong I am.
Watch me jump!

402
00:39:04.925 --> 00:39:05.995
Jump then!

403
00:39:08.775 --> 00:39:10.185
Now you're jumping all right!

404
00:39:38.493 --> 00:39:40.203
This is how to wash your face.

405
00:40:15.265 --> 00:40:16.264
Damn you!

406
00:40:20.100 --> 00:40:21.646
Stop eating!

407
00:40:24.150 --> 00:40:27.700
- We're friends. remember?
- Okay. let's be friends.

408
00:40:41.646 --> 00:40:44.756
You've got arms of iron.
but you've brains of straw.

409
00:40:47.038 --> 00:40:49.178
Stop that. let's get out of here!

410
00:41:00.284 --> 00:41:01.264
This way...

411
00:41:12.565 --> 00:41:13.638
You know what?

412
00:41:14.168 --> 00:41:16.256
I can't help wondering
how old you are.

413
00:41:17.147 --> 00:41:18.780
For your age. you sure are tough.

414
00:41:19.608 --> 00:41:20.543
A necessity.

415
00:41:21.059 --> 00:41:24.845
I've had to be tough to be
able to survive to this age.

416
00:41:25.275 --> 00:41:29.667
Just look at you.
You're weak and useless.

417
00:41:34.362 --> 00:41:37.144
Today was just a bad day.

418
00:41:37.146 --> 00:41:39.922
If I hadn't fallen into the trap.

419
00:41:40.450 --> 00:41:42.166
I'd have beaten them.

420
00:41:43.900 --> 00:41:46.307
Sounds like an excuse.

421
00:41:46.918 --> 00:41:51.546
I forgot to ask why you
couldn't pay for your meal.

422
00:41:52.650 --> 00:41:56.877
That's a long story.
Old man. may I know your name?

423
00:41:58.175 --> 00:41:58.975
I'm Mr. So.

424
00:41:59.600 --> 00:42:04.839
Hey. there's a fellow with the
same name screwing up my life!

425
00:42:06.425 --> 00:42:07.935
It’s all his fault!

426
00:42:09.075 --> 00:42:12.423
- Who are you talking about?
- He's this creep named Beggar So.

427
00:42:12.425 --> 00:42:14.617
My own father asked
this guy to train me.

428
00:42:14.619 --> 00:42:16.112
So you're afraid of him?

429
00:42:16.568 --> 00:42:18.528
Afraid? Of course not!

430
00:42:19.421 --> 00:42:20.872
I have heard rumours.

431
00:42:20.874 --> 00:42:24.473
He's very cunning. violent and mean.

432
00:42:24.475 --> 00:42:25.838
But I’ll show him!

433
00:42:27.059 --> 00:42:29.771
That old fart. Wait until
I see him. I’ll tear him apart.

434
00:42:31.262 --> 00:42:32.898
You'll show the fart. huh?

435
00:42:35.425 --> 00:42:36.957
Hey. just where do you come from?

436
00:42:38.228 --> 00:42:42.754
The sky is my roof and I
sleep where ever I may.

437
00:42:42.756 --> 00:42:47.116
- So you're a bum?
- Everyone calls me Beggar So.

438
00:42:48.375 --> 00:42:49.635
Your name is Beggar So as well?

439
00:42:52.124 --> 00:42:54.124
- Beggar So?
- That's the name.

440
00:43:15.293 --> 00:43:18.583
That was close. Good thing I'm fast.

441
00:43:22.384 --> 00:43:25.674
Not fast enough!
You can't escape from me!

442
00:43:32.393 --> 00:43:36.563
Your father paid me well to train
you and that's what I’m going to do!

443
00:43:42.722 --> 00:43:44.442
How long will this take?

444
00:43:46.547 --> 00:43:48.748
- One day?
- One year exactly.

445
00:43:48.750 --> 00:43:49.830
I'll never make it!

446
00:43:58.912 --> 00:44:01.988
You already have your cash.
so you can relax.

447
00:44:01.990 --> 00:44:05.085
I wouldn't do that.
I’m going to enjoy this!

448
00:44:05.087 --> 00:44:06.086
I’ll see you in hell!

449
00:44:26.034 --> 00:44:27.039
You're strangling me.

450
00:44:35.775 --> 00:44:38.148
Well. you're just a stupid old fool.

451
00:44:38.150 --> 00:44:41.148
You're just an old beggar who likes
to pretend you're a real tiger.

452
00:44:41.150 --> 00:44:43.873
I’ll show you what a tiger's about!

453
00:44:56.500 --> 00:44:58.519
I see your tiger's got a bad paw. huh?

454
00:44:59.498 --> 00:45:00.503
Tiger-Fist!

455
00:45:18.100 --> 00:45:19.444
It’s still there!

456
00:45:36.121 --> 00:45:40.111
All that Kung-Fu looks like dancing.

457
00:45:40.671 --> 00:45:41.670
The Crane attacks!

458
00:45:43.850 --> 00:45:46.798
Crane's Beak. Angry Crane.

459
00:45:46.800 --> 00:45:47.923
Crane eats the Shrimp!

460
00:45:50.350 --> 00:45:54.407
- The Crane Flies.
- How's your head?

461
00:46:08.537 --> 00:46:10.582
Your fingers are
stronger than my teeth!

462
00:46:16.494 --> 00:46:18.234
I'm coming to get you!

463
00:46:20.983 --> 00:46:22.063
You scared me!

464
00:46:22.911 --> 00:46:24.503
Climbing trees to get away now. are we?

465
00:46:25.115 --> 00:46:28.205
What? I’m just using Monkey Kung-Fu.

466
00:46:58.150 --> 00:47:01.773
Ready to learn? Answer! Answer!

467
00:47:01.775 --> 00:47:04.298
Please stop. I want to learn.

468
00:47:05.654 --> 00:47:10.189
But I don't like your
style of recruitment.

469
00:47:34.025 --> 00:47:37.815
Let me down!
I don't want to die like this.

470
00:47:50.150 --> 00:47:51.899
I thought you were
supposed to be a teacher.

471
00:47:52.800 --> 00:47:55.110
But you are trying to kill me.

472
00:47:57.175 --> 00:48:01.023
All students with style
must learn how to fall.

473
00:48:01.025 --> 00:48:03.035
That was only your first lesson.

474
00:48:56.976 --> 00:48:58.512
Trying to escape?

475
00:48:58.514 --> 00:49:00.111
I just wanna take a piss.

476
00:49:00.437 --> 00:49:01.736
So do it there!

477
00:49:17.249 --> 00:49:19.619
From the right jar to the left jar.

478
00:49:27.996 --> 00:49:30.099
The back jar to the right jar.

479
00:49:32.992 --> 00:49:34.712
The back jar to the front jar.

480
00:49:42.056 --> 00:49:43.894
Left jar to the right jar.

481
00:49:45.627 --> 00:49:47.627
The right jar to the front jar.

482
00:49:56.364 --> 00:49:59.048
Left jar to right jar.
right jar to left jar.

483
00:49:59.050 --> 00:50:01.113
I can never finish it!

484
00:50:04.331 --> 00:50:05.491
Continue!

485
00:50:08.362 --> 00:50:10.695
This is torture. Fine!

486
00:50:37.742 --> 00:50:40.439
Fei-Hung! Fei-Hung!

487
00:50:53.869 --> 00:50:56.239
Have a good wash. you old bastard!

488
00:51:28.362 --> 00:51:29.783
Hey you. get out of here.

489
00:51:34.150 --> 00:51:35.718
Do you hear me? Are you deaf?

490
00:51:37.475 --> 00:51:40.248
Are you blind? Can't you see I’m busy.

491
00:51:41.525 --> 00:51:44.635
No hanging around you bum.
Move your ass.

492
00:51:45.550 --> 00:51:49.208
Is this your place?
What if I refuse to move then?

493
00:51:50.690 --> 00:51:53.623
A big mouth and a wet ass.

494
00:51:53.625 --> 00:51:55.767
It should be taught some manners.

495
00:52:00.227 --> 00:52:01.226
How does it feel?

496
00:52:05.405 --> 00:52:06.404
Nice and dry?

497
00:52:08.036 --> 00:52:11.736
Right you twerp! I’ll give you dry!
I’ll shove you in the head first.

498
00:52:22.749 --> 00:52:23.748
Come on...

499
00:52:42.314 --> 00:52:45.907
What's that supposed to be. Kung-Fu?
Who taught you that load of shit?

500
00:52:45.909 --> 00:52:47.535
Who's your master?

501
00:52:47.978 --> 00:52:49.575
No-one calls my father's Kung-Fu shit!

502
00:53:05.993 --> 00:53:09.303
Judging by that. your old
man's Kung-Fu stinks.

503
00:53:09.305 --> 00:53:12.265
I wouldn't ask him to clean my shoes.

504
00:53:18.016 --> 00:53:20.396
I think you'd better call me father.

505
00:53:20.794 --> 00:53:21.962
Go to hell!

506
00:53:29.577 --> 00:53:30.497
Sit down!

507
00:53:31.675 --> 00:53:33.491
Get up! Sit down again!

508
00:53:37.382 --> 00:53:39.322
All my dogs must obey.

509
00:53:47.702 --> 00:53:48.610
Quit playing!

510
00:53:58.019 --> 00:53:59.406
Take my shoes.

511
00:53:59.850 --> 00:54:00.870
What...?

512
00:54:06.121 --> 00:54:08.069
I don't even need to use my hands.

513
00:54:09.293 --> 00:54:11.810
You'd better use them. I’m not scared!

514
00:54:23.716 --> 00:54:24.716
Had enough?

515
00:54:25.665 --> 00:54:27.645
I won't stop until I send
you straight to hell!

516
00:54:41.737 --> 00:54:42.597
Don't come here!

517
00:54:42.969 --> 00:54:43.968
Ah shit!

518
00:54:44.825 --> 00:54:46.825
You've become a cowardly turtle!

519
00:55:02.281 --> 00:55:03.821
Your skull's like butter.

520
00:55:04.215 --> 00:55:08.260
You could study kung-fu for the rest
of your life and still not beat me.

521
00:55:23.197 --> 00:55:25.197
Killing a nobody like you...

522
00:55:25.859 --> 00:55:28.189
would only ruin my reputation.

523
00:55:28.590 --> 00:55:32.430
Crawl between my legs...
and then go home to your pig-sty!

524
00:55:35.131 --> 00:55:36.130
Crawl!

525
00:56:06.052 --> 00:56:07.051
Wait!

526
00:56:09.615 --> 00:56:11.615
Aren't these your pants?

527
00:57:01.656 --> 00:57:04.756
Judging by that. your old
man's Kung-Fu stinks.

528
00:57:05.413 --> 00:57:07.043
I wouldn't ask him to clean my shoes.

529
00:57:16.453 --> 00:57:17.723
Your skull's like butter.

530
00:57:18.412 --> 00:57:22.507
You could study kung-fu for the rest
of your life and still not beat me.

531
00:57:39.005 --> 00:57:41.425
Killing a nobody like you...

532
00:57:41.675 --> 00:57:44.394
would only ruin my reputation.

533
00:57:44.396 --> 00:57:48.423
Crawl between my legs.
then go home to your pig-sty.

534
00:57:48.425 --> 00:57:49.424
Crawl!

535
00:59:05.309 --> 00:59:09.549
You idiot. this wine is very expensive.

536
00:59:10.184 --> 00:59:12.304
It smells good!

537
00:59:14.896 --> 00:59:18.326
Master. enjoy your wine.
I'll dry your clothes.

538
00:59:35.599 --> 00:59:37.989
Hey. why are you so sexy?

539
00:59:52.762 --> 00:59:55.936
- The clothes caught fire...
- It’s on fire!

540
00:59:58.630 --> 01:00:02.390
Oh god! You've burnt
my best cloak I have!

541
01:00:37.493 --> 01:00:39.353
My back!

542
01:01:04.069 --> 01:01:06.589
- My wrists!
- Your wrists are not strong enough.

543
01:01:14.678 --> 01:01:20.519
More rabbit food...
and the tea's weak & cold.

544
01:01:20.521 --> 01:01:21.494
Stay quiet and eat.

545
01:01:22.702 --> 01:01:26.025
Master. you're giving me a headache.

546
01:01:26.027 --> 01:01:27.307
Eat your meal.

547
01:01:35.175 --> 01:01:36.174
What's wrong?

548
01:01:36.850 --> 01:01:39.330
You're so tired you can't
even use your chopsticks?

549
01:03:05.087 --> 01:03:07.287
Master. I’m finished.

550
01:03:08.350 --> 01:03:09.830
That was quick.

551
01:03:10.600 --> 01:03:13.250
Now. use these smaller
cups to empty it again.

552
01:03:15.250 --> 01:03:16.630
Go on.

553
01:03:18.100 --> 01:03:21.130
I wish I'd known about this part first.

554
01:03:28.725 --> 01:03:30.005
This is killing me.

555
01:03:36.425 --> 01:03:37.665
- Hey. Hung...
- Yes?

556
01:03:39.250 --> 01:03:41.130
Crack this walnut for me.

557
01:03:45.323 --> 01:03:48.313
No. you break it like this.

558
01:03:50.340 --> 01:03:51.900
Now you try.

559
01:04:51.450 --> 01:04:56.030
Please. Master!
Haven't I cracked enough?

560
01:04:57.125 --> 01:04:58.725
Master. why don't we go for a walk?

561
01:05:00.512 --> 01:05:01.511
All right...

562
01:05:02.913 --> 01:05:03.760
Open now...

563
01:05:13.884 --> 01:05:16.234
- Master. you're good!
- Of course.

564
01:05:19.397 --> 01:05:24.667
Observe well... place your bets!

565
01:05:25.062 --> 01:05:26.752
Old man. you should leave now.

566
01:05:27.275 --> 01:05:28.274
Leave?

567
01:05:29.000 --> 01:05:31.504
How can I buy good wine
with so little money?

568
01:05:33.399 --> 01:05:36.198
I’ve still got more money to win.

569
01:05:38.434 --> 01:05:43.794
Come on. bet...
Trust me. bet there!

570
01:05:46.197 --> 01:05:50.248
Turn it over!

571
01:05:50.250 --> 01:05:52.323
Hurry up!

572
01:05:52.325 --> 01:05:53.522
Hurry up!

573
01:05:53.524 --> 01:05:55.594
Turn it over!

574
01:05:56.715 --> 01:05:57.755
Quit shouting!

575
01:06:05.281 --> 01:06:09.551
You're amazing. Master. You did it again.

576
01:06:12.162 --> 01:06:13.322
That's great.

577
01:06:14.873 --> 01:06:18.032
Put down your bets.
We're getting rich. It's easy!

578
01:06:18.034 --> 01:06:19.034
You were lucky.

579
01:06:20.193 --> 01:06:21.263
I'll play with you...

580
01:06:22.025 --> 01:06:23.024
in one go!

581
01:06:23.566 --> 01:06:26.776
Right. this is my lucky day.

582
01:06:28.150 --> 01:06:29.020
Come on.

583
01:06:53.319 --> 01:06:54.619
- Choose.
- No problem.

584
01:07:01.678 --> 01:07:02.768
Turn it over.

585
01:07:14.118 --> 01:07:15.268
It's not there.

586
01:07:18.059 --> 01:07:21.459
You think you're quick. huh?
Well. my eyes are quicker.

587
01:07:26.800 --> 01:07:29.382
- So. you're trying to cheat. huh?
- So you're a swindler.

588
01:07:31.809 --> 01:07:35.049
Police is here. run!

589
01:07:35.594 --> 01:07:36.916
They're getting away!

590
01:07:44.771 --> 01:07:49.100
You're a dirty thief.
Give me back my money!

591
01:07:49.102 --> 01:07:53.098
You'll never get your money back!
Do you know who I am?

592
01:07:53.440 --> 01:07:54.890
Who cares!

593
01:07:55.525 --> 01:07:59.880
I’ll tell you who I am.
I’m Iron-Head Rat.

594
01:08:00.712 --> 01:08:01.992
I’ll show you with this brick.

595
01:08:04.999 --> 01:08:06.885
Very hard indeed!

596
01:08:06.887 --> 01:08:07.977
Scared?

597
01:08:09.293 --> 01:08:10.343
Hey. baldy!

598
01:08:11.541 --> 01:08:13.242
Give me back the money!

599
01:08:13.244 --> 01:08:16.322
I don't care who you are! I'll beat you.

600
01:08:16.925 --> 01:08:21.015
I warn you. shitface.
I choose who I bury next!

601
01:08:21.512 --> 01:08:23.060
You don't mind to get hurt. do you?

602
01:08:23.062 --> 01:08:24.497
I’ll let you try my iron head!

603
01:08:45.443 --> 01:08:48.106
Master. his head is too hard!

604
01:08:48.108 --> 01:08:49.613
Don't give up!

605
01:08:49.615 --> 01:08:51.584
Let's see you stop my iron head!

606
01:09:00.362 --> 01:09:01.432
This is fun!

607
01:09:15.325 --> 01:09:17.365
Good. very good.

608
01:09:44.200 --> 01:09:47.572
Bet you never guessed you'd
end up in someone's pants!

609
01:10:19.071 --> 01:10:22.291
An iron hammer for an iron head?

610
01:10:45.100 --> 01:10:46.190
Can you take it?

611
01:10:49.628 --> 01:10:51.698
That's enough. please!

612
01:11:09.191 --> 01:11:11.281
Master. my wrists are breaking!

613
01:11:27.100 --> 01:11:28.970
- Lazy!
- No.

614
01:11:37.225 --> 01:11:40.555
My hands are gonna break!

615
01:11:45.881 --> 01:11:47.881
No more exercises.
Go fetch me some wine.

616
01:11:50.316 --> 01:11:50.911
Yes!

617
01:11:50.913 --> 01:11:52.550
"Ru Yi's Restaurant."

618
01:12:02.278 --> 01:12:03.598
Waiter!

619
01:12:03.600 --> 01:12:04.910
Coming. What do you want?

620
01:12:06.394 --> 01:12:08.933
- Some wine.
- Shall I fill it up?

621
01:12:08.935 --> 01:12:12.473
No. three cups will be enough.

622
01:12:12.475 --> 01:12:13.500
Three cups?

623
01:12:14.800 --> 01:12:16.720
Hurry up. don't just stand there.

624
01:12:48.556 --> 01:12:51.556
Damn it! Where's that
stupid boy with my wine?

625
01:13:00.712 --> 01:13:02.308
Idiot!

626
01:13:08.891 --> 01:13:09.890
That's him!

627
01:13:17.619 --> 01:13:19.279
Old man. who are you?

628
01:13:20.200 --> 01:13:21.760
Who's asking?

629
01:13:25.837 --> 01:13:28.268
Old man. have you heard
of the King of Sticks?

630
01:13:28.962 --> 01:13:31.279
Yes. I have.

631
01:13:31.281 --> 01:13:34.729
Have you ever heard
of Beggar So then?

632
01:13:35.534 --> 01:13:36.534
Beggar So?

633
01:13:37.703 --> 01:13:38.973
In person!

634
01:13:41.162 --> 01:13:42.122
Let's go!

635
01:13:42.591 --> 01:13:45.254
Don't go. He doesn't
look like Beggar So.

636
01:13:45.256 --> 01:13:46.520
- What?
- Look.

637
01:13:50.708 --> 01:13:54.110
He's trembling. he can't
be the real Beggar So.

638
01:14:00.307 --> 01:14:03.626
So you think you're being funny?
I’m not fooled that easily.

639
01:14:04.274 --> 01:14:06.984
But I’m not lying. I am Beggar So!

640
01:15:02.942 --> 01:15:04.730
- Master!
- Give me the wine!

641
01:15:15.040 --> 01:15:16.130
It's water!

642
01:15:23.403 --> 01:15:25.918
Idiot! Now see what you've done!

643
01:15:57.518 --> 01:15:58.418
Master!

644
01:16:32.617 --> 01:16:35.921
They're lucky!
If I ever meet them again.

645
01:16:35.923 --> 01:16:37.630
I’ll kill them both. Let's go!

646
01:17:03.130 --> 01:17:05.330
Cheer up. eat something.

647
01:17:07.072 --> 01:17:10.422
Master. it's all my
fault you were beaten.

648
01:17:10.846 --> 01:17:13.156
It seems bad luck follows you around.

649
01:17:13.824 --> 01:17:18.523
I’ve been through a lot of things.
but until this day...

650
01:17:18.525 --> 01:17:20.588
I've never suffered such
humiliation like that!

651
01:17:21.006 --> 01:17:25.191
He wasn't better than you. but you've
no strength without your wine.

652
01:17:26.518 --> 01:17:28.078
You sure can talk.

653
01:17:29.209 --> 01:17:34.849
True. but if I had been taught better.
I could've beaten that jerk.

654
01:17:36.122 --> 01:17:38.802
You mean to say I’m not
teaching you right?

655
01:17:40.153 --> 01:17:45.643
You're just pushing me around.
You're teaching me how to get beaten.

656
01:17:52.512 --> 01:17:56.917
Your father is without question
an excellent martial arts Master.

657
01:17:56.919 --> 01:18:00.173
His methods are among the best.

658
01:18:00.175 --> 01:18:03.095
So why would he ask me
to teach you my style?

659
01:18:03.881 --> 01:18:05.651
He wants you to torture me.

660
01:18:08.075 --> 01:18:13.315
He asked me because he knows
I’ve got a secret style.

661
01:18:14.009 --> 01:18:15.008
What's that?

662
01:18:15.587 --> 01:18:17.557
The Eight Drunken Gods.

663
01:18:19.466 --> 01:18:23.202
It’s nothing special.
That shows your damned ignorance.

664
01:18:23.706 --> 01:18:30.771
Many people have asked me to teach
them but I turned them all down!

665
01:19:04.994 --> 01:19:09.623
Don't be fooled by my staggering.
there's power inside to kill.

666
01:19:09.625 --> 01:19:14.644
It looks real enough. yet it isn't.
Pretending lets you win.

667
01:19:35.591 --> 01:19:36.951
Clever. isn't it?

668
01:19:38.003 --> 01:19:39.793
Why haven't you shown me it before?

669
01:19:41.139 --> 01:19:43.663
Didn't your father tell you that...

670
01:19:43.665 --> 01:19:46.793
foundation is very important.

671
01:19:47.163 --> 01:19:52.690
I do this because I want you
to have a good foundation.

672
01:19:54.932 --> 01:19:56.868
I think you're ready now.

673
01:19:56.870 --> 01:19:57.633
Really?

674
01:19:57.635 --> 01:20:01.349
To study my style. you'll find it
easier if you have a drink first.

675
01:20:05.325 --> 01:20:06.575
Drink up.

676
01:20:14.084 --> 01:20:15.254
Have another cup.

677
01:20:21.794 --> 01:20:24.204
Fei-Hung. have you ever gone to school?

678
01:20:24.615 --> 01:20:26.555
I've spent a few years
in a private school.

679
01:20:29.561 --> 01:20:30.966
"Drink up the wine."

680
01:20:32.498 --> 01:20:35.775
- "May our cups never rest."
- "For I’ll sing you a song."

681
01:20:36.825 --> 01:20:38.745
"I’ll put your ears to the test."

682
01:20:40.250 --> 01:20:46.495
"Power and wealth are no avail to us.
When only drinking prevails."

683
01:20:47.280 --> 01:20:49.380
Boy. enough. enough.

684
01:20:53.059 --> 01:20:57.339
"Sober men and sages are
lost through the ages."

685
01:20:57.925 --> 01:21:00.305
"All our brave drinkers
shall never die."

686
01:21:02.784 --> 01:21:05.490
"All our brave drinkers shall never die."

687
01:21:05.962 --> 01:21:07.889
"Shing Fung produces
the finest of wines."

688
01:21:09.700 --> 01:21:12.072
"The best soldiers of Shien
Yang are always young."

689
01:21:15.625 --> 01:21:17.823
"Even the King couldn't
stop my drinking."

690
01:21:18.700 --> 01:21:21.169
"Let's drink a toast to
our ship that's sinking."

691
01:21:23.750 --> 01:21:25.946
"With uplifted cup.
I say to the full moon."

692
01:21:29.150 --> 01:21:31.093
"Why does my shadow appear to swoon?"

693
01:21:32.550 --> 01:21:34.780
"Wine in a radiant cup you see."

694
01:21:36.125 --> 01:21:39.273
"Put down that cup the
horses are awaiting thee."

695
01:21:39.275 --> 01:21:42.329
"Fallen on the battlefield.
the soldier says. who will remember me?"

696
01:21:43.575 --> 01:21:44.957
"Who will remember me?"

697
01:21:46.725 --> 01:21:48.202
"Who will remember me?"

698
01:21:59.300 --> 01:22:03.210
The God Lu. the drunkard
with inner strength.

699
01:22:40.262 --> 01:22:45.062
The God Li. the drunken cripple
with the powerful right leg.

700
01:23:11.350 --> 01:23:16.035
The God Jun. the drunkard
holding a pot in his arms.

701
01:23:42.875 --> 01:23:46.897
The God Lan. the drunkard with
the sudden deadly waist attack.

702
01:24:13.812 --> 01:24:17.590
The God Chan. the drunkard
with the swift double-kicks.

703
01:24:46.050 --> 01:24:49.145
The God Tso. the drunkard
with the powerful throat lock.

704
01:25:15.175 --> 01:25:18.476
The God Han. the drunken flute
player with powerful wrists.

705
01:25:38.121 --> 01:25:42.171
The God Miss Ho. the drunken
woman flaunting her body.

706
01:25:49.584 --> 01:25:53.254
Concentrate! This is serious.

707
01:25:53.752 --> 01:25:56.300
Isn't this style for women?

708
01:25:56.302 --> 01:25:59.921
Miss Ho is a woman. yes.
but she is strong. Watch me.

709
01:26:05.459 --> 01:26:06.463
Do like I do!

710
01:26:20.900 --> 01:26:22.320
Continue practicing!

711
01:26:23.075 --> 01:26:24.254
Okay. I will.

712
01:26:24.750 --> 01:26:25.820
Practice hard!

713
01:26:31.250 --> 01:26:33.390
This is for sissies. I won't do it!

714
01:26:38.737 --> 01:26:39.817
Wong Kei-Ying!

715
01:26:40.387 --> 01:26:45.447
Why do you persuade the Bull Head Hill
villagers not to sell me their land?

716
01:26:46.265 --> 01:26:47.765
What was your reason for it?

717
01:26:49.702 --> 01:26:51.849
Was it because of that
business over your son?

718
01:26:52.240 --> 01:26:53.691
That's a personal issue.

719
01:26:54.153 --> 01:26:56.063
It'll be settled in good time.

720
01:26:56.521 --> 01:26:59.181
I'm not responsible.
What is your game?

721
01:27:00.006 --> 01:27:01.029
What is yours?

722
01:27:01.031 --> 01:27:03.223
Mr. Li. why do you want to buy the hill?

723
01:27:05.287 --> 01:27:07.085
As you wish to know. I'll tell you.

724
01:27:07.468 --> 01:27:13.548
That old graveyard up there has been haunting
us for centuries. disturbing family spirits!

725
01:27:14.853 --> 01:27:18.643
They'll get more than $20 per lot.
it's good money for that land.

726
01:27:19.146 --> 01:27:21.219
Then you butt your nose in
where it isn't wanted!

727
01:27:21.221 --> 01:27:23.391
You mean you want to buy the graveyard?

728
01:27:25.142 --> 01:27:28.174
Don't you believe me?
There's a curse on the name of Li!

729
01:27:28.176 --> 01:27:32.451
And it must be exorcised.
I've got three mistresses without children!

730
01:27:32.453 --> 01:27:35.544
I'll be content with a chicken egg.
But they can't produce that!

731
01:27:36.059 --> 01:27:38.524
Maybe you've just become impotent.

732
01:27:43.900 --> 01:27:46.857
You can't hide anything
from me. Mr. Li.

733
01:27:48.000 --> 01:27:49.430
And what's that supposed to mean?

734
01:27:50.352 --> 01:27:53.759
Li Wan-Hao. I think you just
want what's hidden in the hill.

735
01:27:55.025 --> 01:27:56.065
What would that be?

736
01:27:56.550 --> 01:27:58.432
- The coal.
- The coal?

737
01:27:58.434 --> 01:28:00.268
Bull Head Hill contains a rich coal deposit.

738
01:28:00.270 --> 01:28:05.403
You secretly deal with the Coal Company
to make profit from the selling of the coal.

739
01:28:06.524 --> 01:28:09.174
You can fool the villagers.
but you can't fool me!

740
01:28:14.900 --> 01:28:18.470
Since you know it. I won't deny.

741
01:28:18.822 --> 01:28:23.222
If you don't interfere.
I'll give you 20% of the profit.

742
01:28:23.906 --> 01:28:26.846
20%? You'd spend so much on me?

743
01:28:27.125 --> 01:28:31.225
Listen. Li Wan-hao.
the hill belongs to the villagers.

744
01:28:31.653 --> 01:28:34.193
No one can take it away.
get out of here!

745
01:28:35.359 --> 01:28:38.029
Wong Kei-Ying.
you're trying to go against me.

746
01:28:38.275 --> 01:28:41.333
No matter how good your Kung-Fu is.
you are going to pay for this!

747
01:29:00.687 --> 01:29:04.840
$1000 for the death of
Wong Kei-Ying of Fushan.

748
01:29:07.625 --> 01:29:09.235
Wong Kei-Ying?

749
01:29:09.830 --> 01:29:11.735
"Teacher's Birthday Ceremony"

750
01:29:22.425 --> 01:29:23.595
Master.

751
01:29:23.597 --> 01:29:25.397
- Is everything ready for tonight?
- Yes.

752
01:29:30.597 --> 01:29:32.650
Hurry up. there will be
many guests tonight.

753
01:29:39.628 --> 01:29:41.558
Hey. Master Hsu.

754
01:29:44.487 --> 01:29:45.567
Big Funeral?

755
01:29:48.256 --> 01:29:50.123
Are you a dumb masochist?

756
01:29:50.125 --> 01:29:51.924
Coming here looking for more punishment?

757
01:29:51.925 --> 01:29:53.325
Didn't you suffer enough last time?

758
01:29:57.014 --> 01:30:01.239
I just wanna have something
to eat and someone to beat.

759
01:30:01.241 --> 01:30:03.099
Alright. I’ll make you
an extra special dish!

760
01:30:03.100 --> 01:30:04.823
Master. what would it be?

761
01:30:04.825 --> 01:30:06.424
Bamboo shoot and pork.

762
01:30:06.425 --> 01:30:08.422
- Go get my stick.
- Okay.

763
01:30:08.628 --> 01:30:09.627
Pork?

764
01:30:11.525 --> 01:30:12.585
I'll have a piece first.

765
01:30:14.525 --> 01:30:16.765
Right. it tastes good!

766
01:30:17.196 --> 01:30:18.195
Master.

767
01:30:21.362 --> 01:30:22.361
Cheers.

768
01:30:58.850 --> 01:31:01.280
Wow. your teeth are sharp!
They bit right through the bowl.

769
01:31:23.300 --> 01:31:24.299
Now what?

770
01:31:35.465 --> 01:31:38.735
Be careful now. toothy.
Take it easy.

771
01:31:49.624 --> 01:31:52.164
I did tell you to take it easy.

772
01:32:07.414 --> 01:32:08.414
Sit still!

773
01:32:16.587 --> 01:32:18.737
A fart for the King of Sticks.

774
01:32:29.000 --> 01:32:30.680
This is 'Hungry Dogs Eats Shit!'

775
01:32:31.456 --> 01:32:32.456
Not quite!

776
01:32:38.731 --> 01:32:39.821
You like it?

777
01:34:03.125 --> 01:34:04.185
He's drunk!

778
01:34:41.425 --> 01:34:43.785
The old man will like this.

779
01:34:50.425 --> 01:34:54.725
Master. the King of Sticks gave
us wine. It’s free of charge.

780
01:34:59.000 --> 01:35:00.000
Master.

781
01:35:01.334 --> 01:35:02.333
Master.

782
01:35:05.575 --> 01:35:06.605
Master.

783
01:35:07.425 --> 01:35:08.424
Master.

784
01:35:18.550 --> 01:35:21.048
Fei-Hong. one year has passed...

785
01:35:21.575 --> 01:35:25.998
and it’s time for us to
go our separate paths.

786
01:35:26.000 --> 01:35:30.473
I have taught you all the techniques
and the magic of kung fu.

787
01:35:30.475 --> 01:35:33.648
Practice diligently.
master each technique...

788
01:35:33.650 --> 01:35:36.608
The Eight Drunken Gods
is the ultimate Kung-Fu.

789
01:35:36.610 --> 01:35:40.023
My home is the world.
Try not to miss me.

790
01:35:40.025 --> 01:35:41.510
Go home and be a good son.

791
01:35:41.512 --> 01:35:46.185
Remember this. If you ever need me.
I’ll be there. Beggar So.

792
01:35:54.975 --> 01:35:56.574
Master...

793
01:35:56.576 --> 01:36:00.541
Master!

794
01:36:16.846 --> 01:36:17.845
Higher!

795
01:36:24.352 --> 01:36:26.472
- Harder!
- Master Wong!

796
01:36:28.428 --> 01:36:30.626
- Master Wong...
- What is it?

797
01:36:30.628 --> 01:36:34.336
Master Wong. Li and his men
are digging on Bull Head Hill!

798
01:36:34.609 --> 01:36:35.561
Really?

799
01:36:36.343 --> 01:36:39.173
Tell the men I’m going there. Quick!

800
01:36:42.294 --> 01:36:44.389
This way! Quick!

801
01:37:18.512 --> 01:37:19.611
Wong Kei-Ying.

802
01:37:19.613 --> 01:37:23.189
Your skill in Kung-Fu is renowned.
I compliment you.

803
01:37:24.799 --> 01:37:29.669
Who are you? I don't know you.
Why do you want to kill me?

804
01:37:31.009 --> 01:37:34.989
I'm Yen Tieh-hsin.
I kill for money.

805
01:37:35.359 --> 01:37:40.749
Today. I have a worthy opponent.
I'd like to pay you my respects.

806
01:37:42.096 --> 01:37:47.456
I’ve heard of you. The cold-blooded
assassin who'd sell his own brother.

807
01:37:48.484 --> 01:37:49.434
That's me.

808
01:37:51.039 --> 01:37:54.974
But killing me.
you won't find that so easy.

809
01:37:54.976 --> 01:37:57.638
Then I suppose you'll
want to wish me luck.

810
01:38:18.606 --> 01:38:21.626
Hands are for door knobs
and legs break down doors.

811
01:38:31.002 --> 01:38:33.213
30% from the hands.
the rest are from the legs.

812
01:39:16.003 --> 01:39:19.393
Wong Kei-Ying. Are you
ready to meet your death?

813
01:39:32.644 --> 01:39:33.617
Master.

814
01:39:33.619 --> 01:39:35.419
Father. are you alright?

815
01:39:35.421 --> 01:39:37.487
Idiot. you're back?

816
01:39:37.925 --> 01:39:40.355
It’s alright. Don't be afraid. I'm here.

817
01:39:40.966 --> 01:39:44.006
He dares to attack my father?
I’ll give him a good lesson!

818
01:39:47.075 --> 01:39:48.110
You again?

819
01:39:50.375 --> 01:39:54.395
Good. You can help bury
your old man. shitface.

820
01:39:57.175 --> 01:40:01.135
Master Wong. it's too bad you
have such a disgraceful son.

821
01:40:03.400 --> 01:40:05.370
You watch out. or you'll
have a body with no ass!

822
01:40:07.193 --> 01:40:12.323
Dumbass. go and clean pig-stys
or I’ll have to kill you too.

823
01:40:12.812 --> 01:40:15.354
I won't die. bastard.
but the worms'll grow fat on you!

824
01:40:15.631 --> 01:40:20.791
Okay. I give a discount today.
killing two for the price of one!

825
01:40:21.712 --> 01:40:22.712
Up yours!

826
01:40:26.000 --> 01:40:31.473
Wait... wait for me.

827
01:40:31.475 --> 01:40:33.282
Master. what are you doing here?

828
01:40:34.565 --> 01:40:38.311
How can Beggar So
miss a great fight?

829
01:40:38.825 --> 01:40:42.695
Beggar So. it's none of your business.
Go away!

830
01:40:43.500 --> 01:40:48.710
You are mistaken.
This is very much my business.

831
01:40:49.121 --> 01:40:53.678
But don't worry.
I’m not going to fight you.

832
01:40:54.050 --> 01:40:56.410
He is good enough to do it.

833
01:40:58.778 --> 01:41:00.816
Come. Drink first.

834
01:41:41.721 --> 01:41:44.519
Master. this wine is strong.
What kind is it?

835
01:41:45.396 --> 01:41:46.734
San Pien Wine.

836
01:41:47.324 --> 01:41:48.323
I’m drunk!

837
01:42:43.475 --> 01:42:46.815
I’m the God Lu. the drunkard
with inner strength.

838
01:42:58.200 --> 01:42:59.880
The cripple Li!

839
01:43:27.850 --> 01:43:30.781
The drunk with a strong right leg.

840
01:43:32.119 --> 01:43:33.189
The God Lan!

841
01:43:50.812 --> 01:43:55.122
A sudden attack to the waist.
the God Jun!

842
01:43:56.825 --> 01:43:59.305
Holding a pot in his arms.
Han's gone mad!

843
01:44:15.350 --> 01:44:17.840
Well done. the Eight Drunken Gods...

844
01:44:18.827 --> 01:44:22.417
Patience. you've not seen it all yet.

845
01:44:23.528 --> 01:44:24.528
The God Han.

846
01:44:28.928 --> 01:44:31.038
He's the flute player
with the powerful wrists.

847
01:44:59.453 --> 01:45:00.453
Impressive!

848
01:45:02.537 --> 01:45:03.877
Your flute is bent.

849
01:45:04.997 --> 01:45:05.996
The God Tso.

850
01:45:06.987 --> 01:45:10.342
- drunkard with the powerful...
- Throat Lock.

851
01:45:32.697 --> 01:45:34.097
Now your lock is broken.

852
01:45:48.818 --> 01:45:50.068
The Devil's Shadowless Hands.

853
01:45:51.740 --> 01:45:52.990
Yes. you're very observant.

854
01:45:56.021 --> 01:45:57.071
The God Chan!

855
01:46:03.569 --> 01:46:04.919
The God Chan won't reach old age!

856
01:46:22.409 --> 01:46:24.189
Where's the drunken Miss Ho?

857
01:46:25.225 --> 01:46:28.509
Miss Ho... Ho...

858
01:46:34.825 --> 01:46:35.885
Wait!

859
01:46:36.277 --> 01:46:39.223
- Master. there's a problem.
- What?

860
01:46:39.225 --> 01:46:40.475
I didn't bother to learn this!

861
01:46:42.797 --> 01:46:45.867
- Can you teach me now?
- It’s too late!

862
01:47:11.699 --> 01:47:12.759
Fei-Hung!

863
01:47:13.475 --> 01:47:17.385
She'll appear without a shadow.
just perform the actions.

864
01:47:19.990 --> 01:47:24.160
Combine the other 7 styles.
and make your own Miss Ho.

865
01:47:26.159 --> 01:47:28.509
Ho? You want Ho? Sure.

866
01:47:42.247 --> 01:47:43.817
This is called Widow Seeing Lover off.

867
01:47:51.224 --> 01:47:53.854
Woman sitting on a toilet Seat.

868
01:48:01.321 --> 01:48:02.491
You don't sit right!

869
01:48:10.724 --> 01:48:11.884
Putting on Make-up.

870
01:48:15.393 --> 01:48:17.283
Pretty girl looks in the mirror.

871
01:48:18.824 --> 01:48:20.454
These are the famous
Eight Drunken Gods?

872
01:48:21.550 --> 01:48:24.474
So. you think that you're
the only master here.

873
01:48:24.476 --> 01:48:28.626
Everyone has different styles even
they learn from the same master.

874
01:49:58.656 --> 01:50:00.736
The goddess wants a drink.
Come on!

874
01:50:01.305 --> 01:51:01.191
